\section{Qubole Data Service}

Qubole is a data services company who offers cloud services, data management, and data system security to companies.
\begin{center}
  \textit{Qubole Data Service is the first Autonomous Big Data Platform, a comprehensive big data platform that self-manages, self-optimizes and learns from your usage, allowing the data team to focus on business outcomes rather than on managing the platform.}
\end{center}
The BigData Platform in Qubole Data services contains all important elements for companies to process their data, and it is not hard to use. Multiple cloud providers can be chose, the company could select the cloud provider for their own commercial purpose (the most of the cloud providers in Qubole Data Service are open source)\cite{QDS}.
